cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use ufi, please cite it using these metadata."
title: ufi
abstract: >-
  An agent-focused CLI for Ubiquiti UniFi Network over the official local Integration API:
  read-only by default, gated mutations with a reviewed-artifact apply<hash> flow, machine
  -discoverable schema, stable exit codes, and prompt-injection fencing — built to the Agent
  CLI Guidelines.
type: software
authors:
  - given-names: Ryan
    family-names: Wolfe
repository-code: "https://github.com/rnwolfe/ufi"
url: "https://uficli.sh"
license: MIT
keywords:
  - cli
  - ai-agents
  - llm-tools
  - unifi
  - ubiquiti
  - go
